Titolo: Band of Bugs

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Band of Bugs is a turn-based tactics video game developed by NinjaBee. The game includes a level editor, leaderboards, Xbox Live Vision camera support, and multiplayer gameplay. It was released on Xbox Live Arcade on June 20, 2007.On December 3, 2007, a Microsoft Windows version was released. Band of Bugs is also available on Xbox One through the Backward Compatibility program.